# Production API URL (used when running: npm run build)
# IMPORTANT: When the app is served over HTTPS (e.g. on Render), the API URL
# must also be HTTPS. Browsers block mixed content (HTTPS page → HTTP API).
#
# Set this in Render → Your Frontend Service → Environment:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com
#
# If your backend is on Render, use its HTTPS URL (e.g. https://telemed-backend.onrender.com).
# Do not use http://138.68.67.245:8088 for the deployed frontend.
